His final exam was on everything we've seen since the start of the semester. I had 12 chapters to study without anything at the exam. Everytime, he doesn't have the choice to recalculate our grades because more than 50% of people in class failed the exam and sometime he says something and after he says another thing for the same subject . not clear

Le prof. est de loins le pire, que j'ai eu dans mon bac. Il n'a aucun interet dans la reussite de ses étudiants. Il est en retard sans cesse, mal préparé, et la liste longue. Bref conseil, si vous pouvez l'eviter, faites le.
